      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into automotive excellence with this absolute showstopper! This car is in truly mint condition, looking and performing exactly as it did when it first rolled off the lot. It has been meticulously cared for and kept in a climate-controlled environment, making it a rare find for any enthusiast looking for perfection on wheels.",
