      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical secondary market offering. This specimen exhibits an impeccable exterior finish and a curated interior that remains indistinguishable from its original showroom state. Mechanically, the vehicle operates with surgical precision, having undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets the requirements of the most discerning collector. This is an exemplary opportunity to acquire a motorcar in peerless condition.",
